{
  "stem": "6837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- every family got a certain amount.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had yet form before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was able to bake her own bread yet because we had the flour, and we had-- but we still had enough to go by.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were places, bakeries, that you had the card, the ration card, where you went and you picked up whatever that was coming to you, and also the sugar and also the whatever else was to be gotten, but very little.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I played with my nephews and my nieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I loved them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went outside in the streets, and it was May-- beautiful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The flowers were in bloom, and I was young, and I was-- that is so unfair what's happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have the life to live yet, and I don't know what tomorrow is going to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when you're young, you don't take things so seriously, you know, as an older person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was very concerned what's going to be, and most of the family should be together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were very afraid we were going to be separated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They heard a rumor that the youngsters will go to work and the old people and the little ones will stay home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother was worried, where will they go?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What will I do as a young girl?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of work will they give us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what supervision is going to be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it didn't come to that, because after the two weeks, we left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They deported us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, about.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, uh-- there was on the gate, by the-- where the-- that was barricaded, the area, the outside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not in the ghetto, we didn't see that, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, first of all, we had to go through a hold.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
